excellent choice for you. Practicality is central to these L-shaped kitchen layout ideas with island. It features hooks for hanging spoons, in-built shelves for microwaves and ovens and additional storage space to keep all your daily essentials.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The wooden island is a perfect addition to this kitchen and entirely elevates the look. Together with the stools, it forms a comfortable seating area where you can sit down for a quick chat over tea or snacks. You can also have drawers on your island \u2013 to keep your cutlery, napkins and take them out right before eating. Neat, easy on the eye, and sleek \u2013 this L-shaped kitchen with island is just the right fit for you if you have sufficient space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-3 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193006\/sleek-stylish-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg\" alt=\"Sleek stylish l shaped kitchen with island\" data-id=\"28244\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193006\/sleek-stylish-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=28244\" class=\"wp-image-28244\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193006\/sleek-stylish-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193006\/sleek-stylish-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193006\/sleek-stylish-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193006\/sleek-stylish-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">This kitchen design is sure to make everyone stop and stare<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make The Most Of Your Kitchen Space With This Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have a small home or kitchen, the idea of having a kitchen island probably never crossed your mind. But our next design here is proof of how you can transform even a not-so-big kitchen into a functional and stylish space with an island.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>This L-shaped kitchen with island makes the best possible use of space. It gives you all that you could want in a kitchen while making it out-of-the-ordinary at the same time. The colour combination itself makes the kitchen a sight to behold. The island at the entrance works its charm to enhance its look. Not just for keeping and storing food, this also makes for a great area where you can just sit, relax and catch up with your partner after a long day of work.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-4 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193216\/make-the-most-of-your-kitchen-space-with-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-with-island.jpg\" alt=\"Make the most of your kitchen space with l shaped kitchen layout ideas with island\" data-id=\"28245\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193216\/make-the-most-of-your-kitchen-space-with-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-with-island.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=28245\" class=\"wp-image-28245\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193216\/make-the-most-of-your-kitchen-space-with-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-with-island.jpg 940w, https:\/\/me