oads\/2021\/11\/22193347\/a-design-that-proves-the-versatility-of-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg\" alt=\"A design that proves the versatility of l shaped kitchen with island\" data-id=\"28246\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193347\/a-design-that-proves-the-versatility-of-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=28246\" class=\"wp-image-28246\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193347\/a-design-that-proves-the-versatility-of-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193347\/a-design-that-proves-the-versatility-of-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193347\/a-design-that-proves-the-versatility-of-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193347\/a-design-that-proves-the-versatility-of-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">A kitchen island-cum-workstation, what more could one want?\n<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Uplift Your Simple L-Shaped Kitchen With This Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>What we have here is a simple and straightforward kitchen design \u2013 which could\u2019ve looked pretty ordinary had it not been for the matching island our designers created here. The island completely transforms the look and feel of the small L-shaped kitchen.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>To start with, it gives you additional counter space to prepare and store food. But it\u2019s not just that \u2014 add some stools, and you\u2019ll have ready the perfect dining area for days when you\u2019re feeling lazy or super hungry and just want to eat inside the kitchen. Overall, this L-shaped kitchen with island proves how a simple kitchen island can improve the appearance <em>and<\/em> functionality of your space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-6 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193528\/uplift-your-simple-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-wit-island.jpg\" alt=\"Uplift your simple l shaped kitchen layout ideas with island if you love simple and elegant designs\" data-id=\"28247\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193528\/uplift-your-simple-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-wit-island.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=28247\" class=\"wp-image-28247\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193528\/uplift-your-simple-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-wit-island.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193528\/uplift-your-simple-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-wit-island-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193528\/uplift-your-simple-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-wit-island-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193528\/uplift-your-simple-l-shaped-kitchen-layout-ideas-wit-island-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"blocks-gallery-item__caption\">If you love simple and elegant designs, this one\u2019s for you!<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Multi-Level Island To Make Your Kitchen Like No Other<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Want to add an island to your L-shaped kitchen but make it different? Then this idea\u2019s just for you! Here, our designers have created a multi-level kitchen island. Just one level of an island could serve so many purposes, imagine what two could do!&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, you can use the two levels however you like. But the most practical way is to use the lower level for food prep \u2013 given its waist-level height and easy accessibility \u2013 and the upper deck to keep fruits and veggies or as a bar. A multi-level island like this can add the perfect amount of excitement to your kitchen. It will make work easier for you, but that\u2019s not it \u2013 it will also make your kitchen create a fantastic impression on guests and visitors.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-1 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-7 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193716\/a-multi-level-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-to-make-your-kitchen-like-no-other.jpg\" alt=\"A multi-level l shaped kitchen with island to make your kitchen like no other\" data-id=\"28248\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193716\/a-multi-level-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-to-make-your-kitchen-like-no-other.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?attachment_id=28248\" class=\"wp-image-28248\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193716\/a-multi-level-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-to-make-your-kitchen-like-no-other.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193716\/a-multi-level-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-to-make-your-kitchen-like-no-other-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193716\/a-multi-level-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-to-make-your-kitchen-like-no-other-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/22193716\/a-multi-level-l-shaped-kitchen-with-island-to-mak